## 3.3.2. 字符串的拼接

拼接字符串是将两个或多个字符串连接成一个新的字符串。

```c
#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>
#include <string.h>

int main(int argc, char *argv[]) {
    const char* message = "Hello";
    char buffer[256];

    // copy the message to the buffer
    memcpy(buffer, message, strlen(message));

    // print the buffer
    printf("%s\n", buffer);

    // concatenate the message and the buffer
    char* concatenated = malloc(strlen(message) + strlen(buffer) + 1);
    strcpy(concatenated, message);
    strcat(concatenated, buffer);

    // print the concatenated string
    printf("%s\n", concatenated);

    // free the concatenated string
    free(concatenated);

    return 0;
}
```

